keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

# Navigating
unmap d
unmap u
unmap J
unmap K
unmap h
unmap l
unmap r
unmap f
unmap F
unmap <a-f>
unmap yf
map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp
map <c-d>  scrollFullPageDown
map <c-u> scrollFullPageUp
map zh scrollLeft
map zl scrollRight
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode
map R reload
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map hf LinkHints.activateMode action=hover
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map <space>f LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map <space>F LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map df LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink
map yf LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl

# vomnibar
unmap T
unmap o
unmap O
unmap b
unmap B
map S Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map o Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map O Vomnibar.activate
map <space>o Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map <space>O Vomnibar.activateBookmarks

# Manipulating tabs
unmap t
unmap gT
unmap gt
unmap x
unmap X
unmap <a-m>
unmap <a-p>
unmap yt
map gt createTab
map <space>h previousTab
map <space>l nextTab
map gl visitPreviousTab
map bb removeTab
map bh closeTabsOnLeft
map bl closeTabsOnRight
map bo closeOtherTabs
map bm toggleMuteTab
map br restoreTab
map bp togglePinTab
map by duplicateTab
map <space>H moveTabLeft
map <space>L moveTabRight
